result.name: Zerve

reviews.text: Great atmosphere with beer pong tables,nice place to have fun and chill with friends

Drinks are good and so is the vibe, but if you're going for beer pong, don't bother. It's over priced and they give you a strict 10 minute limit... Even if no one is waiting. Nobody finishes in 10 minutes. The PONG place nearby has automated tables and it's 10 minutes stop time. They were missing the cue ball for pool, so we had to play with the 5 ball. Not a big deal, but still... If you're gunna drop a lot of money, I'd expect a little more.
The best bar I ever been to! Great service, good atmosphere, and fun games!
Well decor, buy one get one free before 8pm. Service sucked!
I beat the crowd at 8pm. Got to choose any seats I want 😉
